    "title": "Redirecting",
    "descriptionContent": "Learn how to redirect pages that have moved and how to use redirect to manage versioning",
    "shortDescriptionContent": "",
    "showInTrack": true,
    "iconBanner": null,
    "chapters": [
      {
        "id": 15073,
        "title": "Chapter #1",
        "type": "practiceLevel1",
        "lessons": [
          {
            "title": "Lesson #4",
            "id": 132905,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>A redirect is when a web server tells your browser to go to a different page.</p><p>Redirects are integral. They guide users to the correct content when pages are moved, renamed, or based on specific conditions.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3",
            "id": 132878,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Instead of returning a response via the response object, we call <code>redirect</code> on it.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect();\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"44\" endIndex=\"47\" /><option startIndex=\"47\" endIndex=\"48\" /><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"56\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>res</code>, followed by <code>.</code>, and finally <code>redirect</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy",
            "id": 132906,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>We provide a new route to which the request should be redirected.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"44\" endIndex=\"47\" /><option startIndex=\"47\" endIndex=\"48\" /><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"56\" /><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"69\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>res</code> followed by <code>.</code> and then <code>redirect</code>, <code>\"/new-route\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy - Copy",
            "id": 132908,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>We respond with a new route and, as always, a status code.</p><p>The status code <code>302 Found</code> indicates that the requested resource has been temporarily moved to the URL provided in the response.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"302\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"60\" /><option startIndex=\"60\" endIndex=\"61\" /><option startIndex=\"62\" endIndex=\"74\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>302</code>, followed by <code>,</code>, and finally <code>\"/new-route\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy  Copy",
            "id": 132909,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>We don't have to explicitly set <code>302 Found</code> as it's implicitly set if we use <code>redirect</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"69\" /><option startIndex=\"44\" endIndex=\"47\" /><option startIndex=\"47\" endIndex=\"48\" /><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"56\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>res</code> followed by <code>.</code> and then <code>redirect</code>, <code>\"/new-route\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy",
            "id": 132907,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>When the client receives <code>302 Found</code> along with a new URL, typically, it will redirect by calling the provided endpoint.</p><p>Here, the client will be redirected from <code>\"/old-route\"</code> to <code>\"/new-route\"</code>, receiving a <code>200 OK</code> status and a message.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.status(\" /><text value=\"200\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\").send(\" /><text value=\"&quot;You found me!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"20\" /><option startIndex=\"85\" endIndex=\"97\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>\"/old-route\"</code>, followed by <code>\"/new-route\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #4",
            "id": 132879,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Conversely, a permanent redirect <code>301 Moved Permanently</code> signals a permanent change to the resource's location.</p><p>Let's change our previous temporary redirect to a permanent one.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"301\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"60\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"302\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>301</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #5",
            "id": 132880,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Express also allows routing based on conditional statements. Publishing a new version is easy with redirects.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/:version&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (req.params.version == \" /><text value=\"&quot;1.0&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  res.send(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Version 1.0&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" } \" /><text value=\"else\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/1.0&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"117\" endIndex=\"120\" /><option startIndex=\"120\" endIndex=\"121\" /><option startIndex=\"121\" endIndex=\"129\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>res</code>, followed by <code>.</code>, and finally <code>redirect</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #4 - Copy",
            "id": 132910,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>You can use redirects when working with a router, too.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"router.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"router.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"301\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"6\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>router</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy - Copy",
            "id": 132912,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Redirect from <code>\"/friends\"</code> to <code>\"/homies\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/friends&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"302\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/homies&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/homies&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.status(\" /><text value=\"200\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\").send(\" /><text value=\"&quot;What's up?&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"18\" /><option startIndex=\"85\" endIndex=\"94\" /><option startIndex=\"60\" endIndex=\"69\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&quot;/friends&quot;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>\"/friends\"</code>, followed by <code>\"/homies\"</code>, and finally <code>\"/homies\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #15",
            "id": 132917,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>How do you manually set the status code for a redirect in Express?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>res.redirect(301, \"/new-route\")</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>res.redirect(\"/new-route\", 301)</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\"><code>res.redirect(301, \"/new-route\")</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy - Copy - Copy",
            "id": 132914,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Set the status code for a permanent redirect.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"301\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"60\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"302\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>301</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #17",
            "id": 132919,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Create a temporary redirect from <code>\"/store\"</code> to <code>\"/shop\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/store&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", (req, res) =&gt; {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"302\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/shop&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/shop&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", (req, res) =&gt; {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.status(\" /><text value=\"200\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\").send(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Welcome to the shop!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"16\" /><option startIndex=\"49\" endIndex=\"52\" /><option startIndex=\"54\" endIndex=\"61\" /><option startIndex=\"77\" endIndex=\"84\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&quot;/store&quot;\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"301\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>\"/store\"</code> followed by <code>302</code> and then <code>\"/shop\"</code>, <code>\"/shop\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          }
        ]
      }
